answers.body_markdown:
`by viewModels(...)` is part of [`fragment-ktx`][1] library, it&#39;s a convienience short hand for creating a `lazy` delegate obtaining `ViewModels`.

    // creates lazy delegate for obtaining zero-argument MyViewModel
    private val viewModel : MyViewModel by viewModels()
    // it&#39;s functionally equal to:
    private val viewModel by lazy {
        ViewModelProviders.of(this).get(MyViewModel::class.java)
    }

    // with factory:
    private val viewModel : MyViewModel by viewModels{ getViewModelFactory() }
    // is equal to:
    private val viewModel by lazy {
        ViewModelProviders.of(this, getViewModelFactory()).get(MyViewModel::class.java)
    }    

  [1]: https://developer.android.com/kotlin/ktx#fragment

